[[File:Jon_Knoles.jpg|thumb|Jon Knoles.]]
'''Jon Knoles''' is a game developer, artist, designer, and animator who has worked on numerous ''Star Wars'' video games for [[LucasArts]].

He contributed additional art for ''[[Star Wars: Rebel Assault]]'' including designing the vehicle cockpits; he was also filmed as the character of [[Thurlow Harris]].<ref>''[[Star Wars: Rebel Assault: The Official Insider's Guide]]''</ref>

Knoles was used as the model for [[Dash Rendar/Legends|Dash Rendar]] for his [[Star Wars Customizable Card Game|CCG]] card.

